f5a13fbbf2a26342a043474b5911ad4949e6b61f36116197e9c614d2e399f4dcb6adbab08376764756d68d45cfd55215dd49aa5cdfe5926b61d928a8424ba767  0001-Use-qmlplugindump-qt5.patch"
